data.title: June Temperatures in Saskatchewan
data.meta_description: Average June temperatures for places in Saskatchewan, including lists of monthly high and low temperatures.
data.text:
Average temperatures for June at cities, towns and lakes throughout Saskatchewan are given below.

You can jump to a separate table for each section of the province: Southern, Central and Northern Saskatchewan.

The tables list the normals for maximum and minimum monthly temperatures, in degrees Celsius and Fahrenheit, based on weather data collected from 1981 to 2010.
